The State moves to dismiss and read in counts 2 through 6.  Motion granted.
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three and one-half (3.5) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Have no contact with Joshua Reed, Heritage Apartments, Walmart in Manitowoc, The Crossing in Manitowoc, 1516 N. 9th Street in Manitowoc and with Eric Alaparet;
2) Maintain fulltime employment or work search;
3) AODA assessment and follow through;
4) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
5) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
6) Provide DNA sample;
7) Any other counseling as deemed appropriate by the agent;
8) spend ninety (90) days in the county jail, under the Huber Law, commencing immediately upon completion of the condition time in 15 CM 300;
9) pay restitution of $650.00 to The Crossing at 814 Washington Street, Manitowoc, WI, joint and several with Joshua Reed;
10) Pay court costs;
11) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
